    ClassDeclaration, FieldDeclaration, MethodDeclaration

    public class InstanceDeclaration
extends VariableDeclaration
    Variable extension that represents the declaration of a field or method. Contains the modifiers for visibility and whether or not the field/method is static.
    Since:
    v0.1 Jan 5, 2014 at 9:10:49 PM
    Version:
